net.zethmayr.benjamin.spring.common.mapper.base

Interface PsSetterFactory<O>

  • Type Parameters:
    O - The JDBC type of values set
    Functional Interface:
    This is a functional interface and can therefore be used as the assignment target for a lambda expression or method reference.

    @FunctionalInterface
public interface PsSetterFactory<O>
    Implementations (such as included defaults) can create type-safe value setters for PreparedStatement fields.
